# Cloudflare Pages redirects.
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/

# Strip trailing slashes so they match Astro's `trailingSlash: 'never'`
# canonicals. With `build.format: 'file'` (dist/blog.html, not
# dist/blog/index.html), `/blog/` would 404 on its own — this rule
# 301s it back to `/blog` so old inbound links keep resolving.
/blog/ /blog 301
/code/ /code 301
/info/ /info 301
/blog/*/ /blog/:splat 301
/code/*/ /code/:splat 301
